[Episode 1]

2
00:00:21,720 --> 00:00:23,320
[East Dance Hall]

3
00:00:50,020 --> 00:00:51,600
[Xinxin]

4
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,960
It's rather late.

5
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,720
What if your old man finds out?

6
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:56,560
He will take a concubine tomorrow.

7
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:58,320
He doesn't care about me.

8
00:00:58,480 --> 00:00:59,640
Why,

9
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:02,320
are you getting jealous, Mrs. Fang Fei?

10
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:28,600
Master.

11
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,080
You wench.

12
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:38,000
Are you sure that's true?

13
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:39,600
Master.

14
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:40,920
If I have no evidence,

15
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,960
how could I...?

16
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,040
Even if it's true,

17
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,560
you think I'm glad to know it?

18
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,520
I married you

19
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:49,000
not to cause trouble.

20
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,480
I'm sorry, Master.

21
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:52,760
Hmph.

22
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:01,440
Fang Fei.

23
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,880
It's not your time to die.

24
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:06,960
I must settle some old scores
with you first.

25
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,780
[Palms on Love]

26
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:48,190
[Adapted from the online novel,
The Age of Wind and Rain]

27
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,520
[The White Flower Embrocation]

28
00:02:58,640 --> 00:02:59,680
Extra!

29
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,880
The rich merchant Xue Zhaokun

30
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,040
died from sudden disease.

31
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,200
Extra!

32
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,240
The rich merchant Xue Zhaokun

33
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,520
died from sudden disease.

34
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:22,040
Mrs. Yun Lian is such a jinx.

35
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,720
Master died shortly after marrying her.

36
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:25,680
Madam Xue wants to kick her out.

37
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,680
But she kneels here
and refuses to leave.

38
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,480
When Mr. Xue comes back,

39
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,000
he will handle her.

40
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:37,160
What exactly happened?

41
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,440
I didn't see this coming.

42
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,360
Hand salute!

43
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,640
At ease.

44
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,160
Governor.

45
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,640
Your mourning clothes are ready.

46
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:46,320
Money took his life.

47
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,920
No need to burn joss paper for him.

48
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,440
Governor.

49
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,680
I heard

50
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,480
the new concubine, Mrs. Yun Lian,

51
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,960
is a young, beautiful vixen.

52
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:03,320
She married your father for money.

53
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,920
I'm not surprised.

54
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:10,160
And such an evil woman

55
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,200
should burn.

56
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,920
Since my father died,

57
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:36,080
you should join him.

58
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:50,840
Let go of me.

59
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:51,960
Let go.

60
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:54,200
I have nothing to do with his death.

61
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,240
This voice...

62
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,200
Could it be her?

63
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,160
Xue Dongfeng.

64
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,360
I want to be with you forever.

65
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,360
When we return home,

66
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,520
will you marry me?

67
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:36,240
Ji Lianyun?

68
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,960
My father took you

69
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:53,880
as his sixth concubine?

70
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,800
Why?

71
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,000
You broke up with me

72
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:13,440
to marry my father, didn't you?

73
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:16,680
Speak.

74
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:19,720
Dongfeng.

75
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,240
Dongfeng.

76
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:24,040
Let me go.

77
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:27,000
Don't think you can get away with this.

78
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,120
What do you want?

79
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,240
I've married your father.

80
00:07:41,340 --> 00:07:42,920
I am now his concubine.

81
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,560
Mrs. Yun Lian.

82
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,440
Drop your hypocrisy.

83
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,360
It makes me sick.

84
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,480
Let me go!

85
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,480
Before I returned,

86
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:53,400
I had heard
that you used to be a singer.

87
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,320
A charming,

88
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,240
flirtatious,

89
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,200
and vain woman.

90
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:59,160
And you tried so hard
to marry my father.

91
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,280
But that is not the whole truth.

92
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,840
You're not just a singer.

93
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:06,560
You're also my ex-girlfriend,
Ji Lianyun.

94
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,520
Shut up.

95
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:12,360
I've already forgotten the past.

96
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,760
And remember.

97
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:15,760
My name is Yun Lian.

98
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,920
I hope you can forget the past too.

99
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:19,440
It's good for both of us.

100
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:21,720
Stop.

101
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,720
Close the door.

102
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,640
Let's set things straight before you go.

103
00:08:41,680 --> 00:08:43,320
Fine, I'll make it clear.

104
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:44,720
I love your father.

105
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,160
I love his money even more.

106
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:47,920
If you hadn't told me

107
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,880
you were a poor student,

108
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:52,640
I might have married you instead.

109
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:32,200
♪I'm waiting for the rain
to wet the city♪

110
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:35,400
♪At dusk♪

111
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:39,960
♪As I ran into someone I missed
at the street corner♪

112
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:43,480
♪Old memories flashed♪

113
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:47,080
♪If I can shout that I miss you♪

114
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:51,080
♪I'll be waiting for the sunshine
in the rain♪

115
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:57,680
♪If your heart is as cold as ice♪

116
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:02,720
♪My heart will call for you♪

117
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:06,520
♪Are you as resolute as I am♪

118
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:10,480
♪You wake me up to see you♪

119
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:13,720
♪I'm sure your heart will be soft♪

120
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:17,340
♪You approach me in the name of love♪

121
00:10:17,340 --> 00:10:21,520
♪As time goes by, I realize
there's no time like the present♪

122
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:26,600
♪I have no regrets when being with you♪

123
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:29,240
♪And you're like the rising wind♪

124
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:32,800
♪I ask you not to leave me
in the name of love♪

125
00:10:33,210 --> 00:10:37,720
♪Wind blows and we part ways in silence♪

126
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,960
♪And you're like the cloud♪

127
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:44,510
♪Moving closer or farther away from me♪
